docs/sdp-cli-findings-report.md:8:This report consolidates four bugs and one process issue discovered in sdp-cli during production use on CypherClaw. All findings are backed by evidence from the runtime state DB. Fix #1 has already been pulled in (`98da2b4`). The rest are open.
